{"tid":1719610,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黎明行動指出左一個問題","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:04:53.000Z","uid":33709,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a73980e316cb1d53313738d47a5531deca0d2f68","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"大家眼見呢幾日既黎明行動 成日有港豬/藍絲出黎清路障 仲要幫曱甴手追捕<br />\n今日大西北仲出動埋鄉黑<br />\n大家見好似好多人支持黎明行動 但落過場既就知 <br />\n真正做野既人寥寥可數 因為大部份都係港豬/企埋一邊等人做野既和理非<br />\n<br />\n大西北鄉黑問題就唔講啦 都係要打殘佢地<br />\n想講既係港豬同藍絲既問題 我地要諗下點樣令呢班人轉向我地呢邊<br />\n後勤/和理非既手足要做多啲文宣 量要多之餘 質都要開始提升 從不同既方向去滲透 去改變佢地<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jygd9mS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjygd9mS.png&h=150cc401&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7bcf45b3e873a60f7bc87237ad455360dfd2e37","tid":1719610,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"拒做休息撚 次次休息都無好結果"},{"pid":"d4caffe6c7b6f0dc364770139a933c43f9f7d6a6","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7bcf45b3e873a60f7bc87237ad455360dfd2e37","tid":1719610,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"拒做休息撚 次次休息都無好結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔係叫你休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要後勤/和理非手足諗下點叫多啲人轉向<br />\n就算唔支持 都唔會反對"},{"pid":"ef3497eced0f08eab2bbecc398f40311e3ce2dd0","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"同埋黎明行動同一兩日咁成功 係因為快閃 班狗好難部署<br />\n但當你第三四日都係同一個時間 地點 佢地就好易埋伏到手足 <br />\n所以最緊要係「出奇不意」"},{"pid":"f335e3ea7012a14f31b35d5ed383b86fcb30873f","tid":1719610,"uid":135390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得要揾d有番咁上下年紀既出黎同佢地理論<br />\n將所有責任推番比政府<br />\n叫佢地一齊鬧番個政府點解唔肯答應五大訴求<br />\n依家搞到佢地係因為個政府唔肯答應<br />\n一早答應就唔會搞到依家咁"},{"pid":"f3ea9e98e3ed86920bb9a65983bc29d721a8a45b","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b08714887017b54dee2ab83171019156470127c","tid":1719610,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"34d77c0a25cbce864ad7363cab453ecbaafb5b2d","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":1,"disl