bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0crxFyb.jpg&h=9cab4f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jtz3Ndd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtz3Ndd.jpg&h=16d582d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS2Ekyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS2Ekyf.jpg&h=0739eabb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2LnijX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2LnijX.jpg&h=e88e7e85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGCtdTj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGCtdTj.jpg&h=d91c5307&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCLFPrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCLFPrQ.jpg&h=501c54d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉貼自巴打<br />\n【比警察睇既文宣】3萬警力都返唔到工，我要警察做乜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1715926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1715926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"70c4f498c277493e1ea3dee3fe3fba30d57b989f","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b199f9fe75968e417e0dc2d73ea9653982039032","tid":1719610,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:02:29.000Z","msg":"通常應該係驚被點相日後被捕<br />\n派面巾黑外套有無得諗 幫佢地black bloc"},{"pid":"7ead10a09ce7eeff2bb3cc443231b835cdb80951","tid":1719610,"uid":92340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"傻既<br />\n支持罷工既一係留係屋企<br />\n一係去堵路<br />\n一係去塞鐵<br />\n再唔係悶聲返工<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲唔支持既就係你地出到去要面對既人<br />\n即係藍絲，佢地當然會清路障<br />\n面對面既機會多咗，衝突自然多"},{"pid":"421588d7f99f7144e4e60605fa1763e2635d089b","tid":1719610,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9820428aa9cf444c2fafe258c129628524271bcb","tid":1719610,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178b639e295e729e5a91b4a7948bcde707f1d45b","tid":1719610,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"俾意見? 無意見可俾<br />\n因為你已經講出問題 黃既民意係壓倒性 但實際做野既人太少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口遁師可以話係呢場運動入面最自私 最垃圾既負資產<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1715473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1715473</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負評多過正評 呢個死局黎 有民意又點? <br />\n永遠得少數後生仔做野 其他人口遁 <br />\n<br />\n你班中環友打緊飛機既同時 暴大學生殊死抵抗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/euLBqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/euLBqS</a><br />\n<br />\n中環友救人啊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/evwhuT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/evwhuT</a><br />\n<br />\n我兩個月前開既post<br />\n而家仲適用<br />\n<br />\n林鄭根本判斷100%正確 拉哂你班垃圾就得 因為你地惡唔出咩樣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530539</a>"},{"pid":"fea1e3dc68e85be352ee3cf18ef1f4126efb4b59","tid":1719610,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"每人屋企帶一袋垃圾出嚟拋係馬路上面"},{"pid":"b010a412e0252ec9a66ddff08064ef8c9751dd41","tid":1719610,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"係想討論點樣令中間派加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}